<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_42b2496d-3136-4269-95af-aff4a630997d" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B2F2</sptc><title id="_0f49f302-ad1c-4f55-b0c6-b8f37db42ecc">Heated water installations</title><archive-num>2019: BF2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_12645925-46c7-4e84-8ed3-56f5b35b44d5" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_687ddc65-3b22-49e2-b19e-bdfd5fb8abc7">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_73985402-5041-4646-aa16-565a0fa201a7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> supply must be conveyed through <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_fd6915f7-f8cb-4a32-be3d-2e2d67edb4b4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> installations in a way that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_31a6bcda-11fd-4800-9751-cd85ad713c97">minimises any adverse impact on building occupants, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_17553ee8-9fe7-426f-8c73-662843b18051" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator’s</xref> infrastructure, property and the environment; and</li><li id="_9b3cbe69-03ec-44e8-81b1-052a85c71346">facilitates the conservation of water.</li></ol></subclause></clause>